      "x": 65,
      "y": 844,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: GCD(48, 64) = 16\nStep 2: 48/16 : 64/16 = 3 : 4\n\n  48 : 64\n  ÷16  ÷16\n   3 :  4\n\nTRICK:\nKeep halving both sides:\n48:64 → 24:32 → 12:16 → 6:8 → 3:4\n\nAnswer: 3 : 4 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
