    {
      "id": "el_28",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 844,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total parts = 2+3+5 = 10\nStep 2: A=(2/10)x1500=300\n        B=(3/10)x1500=450\n        C=(5/10)x1500=750\n\n  |██ A ██|███ B ███|█████ C █████|\n  |◄─ 2 ──►|◄── 3 ──►|◄──── 5 ────►|\n\nTRICK:\n1 part = 1500/10 = 150\nA=2x150=300, B=3x150=450, C=5x150=750\n\nAnswer: A=300, B=450, C=750 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
