    {
      "id": "el_33",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 860,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 1/2 : 1/4 : 1/5 : 1/7\nStep 2: LCM(2,4,5,7)=140, multiply each:\n  70 : 35 : 28 : 20\nStep 3: Min = 70+35+28+20 = 153\n\n  ×140→ |███ 70 ███|██ 35 ██|█ 28 █|█ 20 █|\n\nTRICK:\nMultiply all fractions by LCM of denoms\nto instantly clear fractions.\nMin pens = sum of ratio parts\n\nAnswer: 153 pens ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
