      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 1/2 : 1/4 : 1/5 : 1/7\nStep 2: LCM(2,4,5,7)=140, multiply each:\n  70 : 35 : 28 : 20\nStep 3: Min = 70+35+28+20 = 153\n\n  ×140→ |███ 70 ███|██ 35 ██|█ 28 █|█ 20 █|\n\nTRICK:\nMultiply all fractions by LCM of denoms\nto instantly clear fractions.\nMin pens = sum of ratio parts\n\nAnswer: 153 pens ✓",
