      "id": "el_38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1212,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Make B same → LCM(3,5)=15\n  A:B = 2:3 → x5 → 10:15\n  B:C = 5:7 → x3 → 15:21\nStep 2: A:B:C = 10:15:21\n\n  A:B = 10:15\n        B:C = 15:21\n  A : B : C = 10:15:21\n\nTRICK:\nB common term: LCM(3,5)=15\nMultiply each ratio to equalize B\nFor 4+ ratios: abc : xbc : xyc : xyz\n\nAnswer: 10 : 15 : 21 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
