      "y": 1212,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 3:5 = x:25\nStep 2: Cross multiply: 3x25 = 5x\n        75 = 5x → x = 15\n\n  3 : 5  =  x : 25\n  3×25   =  5×x\n   75    =  5x  → x=15\n\nTRICK:\nMultiplier = 25/5 = 5\nx = 3 x 5 = 15\nVerify: 3/5 = 15/25 ✓\n\nAnswer: x = 15 ✓",
