      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1212,
      "width": 224,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: a:x = x:c → x^2 = a x c\nStep 2: x^2 = 4 x 25 = 100\nStep 3: x = sqrt(100) = 10\n\n  4 : [10] : 25\n  4/10 = 10/25 = 2/5 ✓\n\nTRICK:\nMean Proportional = sqrt(a x c)\n= sqrt(4 x 25) = sqrt(100) = 10\nVerify: 4:10 = 10:25 ✓\n\nAnswer: 10 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
