      "y": 1593,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: a:b = b:x → x = b^2/a\nStep 2: x = 12^2/4 = 144/4 = 36\n\n  4 : 12 = 12 : [36]\n  ratio = 1:3 = 1:3 ✓\n\nTRICK:\nThird Proportional = b^2/a\n= 144/4 = 36\nVerify: 4:12 = 12:36 → 1:3 = 1:3 ✓\n\nAnswer: 36 ✓",
