      "y": 1593,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 3:7 = 9:x, cross multiply\nStep 2: 3x = 7x9 = 63 → x = 21\n\n  3 : 7 = 9 : [21]\n  3×21 = 63 = 7×9 ✓\n\nTRICK:\nFourth Proportional = b x c / a\n= 7 x 9 / 3 = 21\nVerify: 3:7 = 9:21 ✓\n\nAnswer: 21 ✓",
