    {
      "id": "el_63",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1593,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=3k, B=4k, C=7k\n  A/B=3/4, B/C=4/7, C/A=7/3\nStep 2: LCM(4,7,3)=84, multiply each:\n  63 : 48 : 196\n\n  3/4 : 4/7 : 7/3\n  ×84→ 63 : 48 : 196\n\nTRICK:\nPlug ratios as fractions, then\nmultiply all by LCM of denominators\nto clear fractions instantly.\n\nAnswer: 63 : 48 : 196 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
