      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=3k, B=4k, C=7k\n  A/B=3/4, B/C=4/7, C/A=7/3\nStep 2: LCM(4,7,3)=84, multiply each:\n  63 : 48 : 196\n\n  3/4 : 4/7 : 7/3\n  ×84→ 63 : 48 : 196\n\nTRICK:\nPlug ratios as fractions, then\nmultiply all by LCM of denominators\nto clear fractions instantly.\n\nAnswer: 63 : 48 : 196 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
