    {
      "id": "el_68",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1959,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: More pens → More cost (DIRECT)\nStep 2: 5/60 = 8/x\nStep 3: x = 60 x 8/5 = Rs.96\n\n  5 pens ──→ Rs.60\n  8 pens ──→ Rs.??\n  ? = 60 × 8/5 = 96\n\nTRICK:\nUnit price = 60/5 = Rs.12/pen\n8 pens = 8 x 12 = Rs.96\n\nAnswer: Rs.96 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
