      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: More pens → More cost (DIRECT)\nStep 2: 5/60 = 8/x\nStep 3: x = 60 x 8/5 = Rs.96\n\n  5 pens ──→ Rs.60\n  8 pens ──→ Rs.??\n  ? = 60 × 8/5 = 96\n\nTRICK:\nUnit price = 60/5 = Rs.12/pen\n8 pens = 8 x 12 = Rs.96\n\nAnswer: Rs.96 ✓",
