        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 13L mixture (M:W=3:2)\n  Remove 3L: 10L left\n  Milk=10x3/5=6, Water=10x2/5=4\nStep 2: Add 3L milk: Milk=9, Water=4\n\n  [M=7.8 W=5.2] -3L→ [M=6 W=4] +3M→ [M=9 W=4]\n  Ratio: 3:2  →  3:2  →  9:4\n\nTRICK:\nRemoved 3L has same ratio 3:2\nMilk left=13x3/5-3x3/5=6, +3=9\nWater left=13x2/5-3x2/5=4\n\nAnswer: New ratio = 9 : 4 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
