      "x": 65,
      "y": 2308,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Salaries of Ram and Sham are in ratio 4:5. If each salary\nis increased by Rs.5000, the new ratio becomes 50:60. Find\nSham's present salary.",
      "fontSize": 13,
