      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let salaries = 4x and 5x\nStep 2: (4x+5000)/(5x+5000) = 50/60\n  Cross: 240x+300000=250x+250000\n  10x=50000 → x=5000\nStep 3: Sham = 5(5000)+5000 = 30000\n\n  Before: 4x : 5x     = 4:5\n  After:  4x+5k : 5x+5k = 5:6\n  Solve → x=5000\n\nTRICK:\n50:60 = 5:6, so new ratio = 5:6\nDiff increased from x to 1000+x\nSolve: 5x+5000 and 6x+6000 pattern\n\nAnswer: Sham's salary = Rs.30,000 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
