    {
      "id": "el_93",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2357,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Multiply antecedents: 2x4x6=48\nStep 2: Multiply consequents: 3x5x7=105\nStep 3: GCD(48,105)=3 → 16:35\n\n  (2:3) × (4:5) × (6:7)\n  = (2×4×6) : (3×5×7)\n  = 48 : 105 = 16 : 35\n\nTRICK:\nCompounded ratio = product/product\nSimplify before multiplying:\n2x4x6 : 3x5x7 = 48:105 = 16:35\n\nAnswer: 16 : 35 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
