      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Multiply antecedents: 2x4x6=48\nStep 2: Multiply consequents: 3x5x7=105\nStep 3: GCD(48,105)=3 → 16:35\n\n  (2:3) × (4:5) × (6:7)\n  = (2×4×6) : (3×5×7)\n  = 48 : 105 = 16 : 35\n\nTRICK:\nCompounded ratio = product/product\nSimplify before multiplying:\n2x4x6 : 3x5x7 = 48:105 = 16:35\n\nAnswer: 16 : 35 ✓",
