      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Duplicate = square both\n  3^2 : 5^2 = 9 : 25\nStep 2: Sub-duplicate = sqrt both\n  sqrt(3) : sqrt(5)\n\n  3 : 5\n  Dup:     3² : 5²   = 9 : 25\n  Sub-dup: √3 : √5\n  Trip:    3³ : 5³   = 27 : 125\n\nTRICK:\nDuplicate: a^2 : b^2\nSub-duplicate: sqrt(a) : sqrt(b)\nTriplicate: a^3 : b^3\n\nAnswer: Dup=9:25, Sub-dup=sqrt3:sqrt5 ✓",
