      "x": 535,
      "y": 2816,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total = 50+55+75 = Rs.180\nStep 2: Ratio 3:4:5, parts=12\n  Amit=(3/12)x180=45, Raju=60, Ram=75\nStep 3: Amit paid 50, should pay 45\n  Amit overpaid by Rs.5\n\n  Fair:  |█ 45 █|██ 60 ██|███ 75 ███|\n  Paid:  |█ 50 █|█ 55 ██|███ 75 ███|\n  Diff:    +5     -5        0\n\nTRICK:\n1 part = 180/12 = 15\nFair: 45, 60, 75\nDiff: 50-45=+5 (overpaid)\n\nAnswer: Amit gets back Rs.5 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
